  "detailed_description": "In Alphageddon, you are the creator of a planet infested by pesky bugs, also known as human beings. Your only option is to, then, make sure they are killed off and removed from your perfect creation. They won't give up that easily, though...<br><br>Alphageddon is a short experimental game, where all levels brings you different game play mechanics, mixing storytelling, fast reflexes, strategy and lots of fire and destruction.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894730/extras/299e45c00b6e7aae22d45c9e28f99cf9.poster.avif?t=1769466054\" width=504 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894730/extras/299e45c00b6e7aae22d45c9e28f99cf9.webm?t=1769466054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894730/extras/299e45c00b6e7aae22d45c9e28f99cf9.mp4?t=1769466054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game is divided into 6 levels:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li> 3 main stories episodes<br>    </li><li> 2 harder arcade modes that you can play for as long as you want<br>    </li><li> 1 secret level</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "In Alphageddon, you are the creator of a planet infested by pesky bugs, also known as human beings. Your only option is to, then, make sure they are killed off and removed from your perfect creation. They won't give up that easily, though...<br><br>Alphageddon is a short experimental game, where all levels brings you different game play mechanics, mixing storytelling, fast reflexes, strategy and lots of fire and destruction.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894730/extras/299e45c00b6e7aae22d45c9e28f99cf9.poster.avif?t=1769466054\" width=504 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894730/extras/299e45c00b6e7aae22d45c9e28f99cf9.webm?t=1769466054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894730/extras/299e45c00b6e7aae22d45c9e28f99cf9.mp4?t=1769466054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game is divided into 6 levels:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li> 3 main stories episodes<br>    </li><li> 2 harder arcade modes that you can play for as long as you want<br>    </li><li> 1 secret level</li></ul>",
